\c 4
\s Ukulingwa kukaJesu
\p
\v 1 Khona uJesu wakhokhelelwa\x + Mark. 1.12,13. Luka 4.1-13.\x* nguMoya enkangala, ukuze alingwe ngudiyabhola\x + 1 Kho. 18.12. Hez. 3.12.\x*.
\v 2 Esezile ukudla insuku ezingamatshumi amane lobusuku obungamatshumi amane\x + 1 Kho. 19.8.\x*, ekucineni walamba.
\v 3 Kwasekusiza kuye umlingi wathi: Uba uyiNdodana kaNkulunkulu\x + 14.33.\x*, tshono ukuthi lamatshe abe yizinkwa.
\v 4 Kodwa yena waphendula wathi: Kulotshiwe \add ukuthi\add*: Umuntu kayikuphila ngesinkwa sodwa, kodwa ngalo lonke ilizwi eliphuma emlonyeni kaNkulunkulu\x + Dute. 8.3.\x*.
\p
\v 5 Udiyabhola wasemthatha\x + Luka 4.9-12.\x* wamusa emzini ongcwele, wasemmisa engqongeni yethempeli\x + Neh. 11.1.\x*,
\v 6 wasesithi kuye: Uba uyiNdodana kaNkulunkulu\x + 14.33.\x*, ziwisele phansi; ngoba kulotshiwe ukuthi: Uzalaya ingilosi zakhe ngawe, besezikuphatha ngezandla, hlezi loba nini ukhube unyawo lwakho elitsheni\x + Hlab. 91.11,12.\x*.
\v 7 UJesu wathi kuye: Kulotshiwe futhi \add ukuthi\add*: Ungayilingi iNkosi uNkulunkulu wakho\x + Dute. 6.16.\x*.
\p
\v 8 Udiyabhola wabuya wamusa entabeni ende kakhulu, wamtshengisa imibuso yonke yomhlaba lokukhazimula kwayo\x + Luka 4.5-8.\x*,
\v 9 wathi kuye: Zonke lezizinto ngizakunika zona, uba uwela phansi ungikhonza.
\v 10 UJesu wasesithi kuye: Suka, Sathane\x + 1 Lan. 21.1.\x*! Ngoba kulotshiwe \add ukuthi\add*: Uzakhothamela eNkosini uNkulunkulu wakho, njalo uzakhonza yona yodwa\x + Dute. 6.13. Dute. 10.20. 1 Sam. 7.3.\x*.
\v 11 Udiyabhola wasemyekela; njalo khangela, kwafika ingilosi zasezimsebenzela\x + 26.53. Luka 22.43. Heb. 1.14.\x*.
\s UJesu uqala ukusebenza eGalili
\p
\v 12 Kwathi uJesu esezwile ukuthi uJohane\x + Mark. 1.14. Luka 3.20. Joha. 3.24.\x* unikelwe \add entolongweni\add*, wasuka waya eGalili\x + Luka 4.14,31. Joha. 4.43. Mat. 9.1.\x*;
\v 13 wasesuka eNazaretha\x + 2.23.\x*, weza wahlala eKapenawume engaselwandle, emingceleni yakoZebuloni leyakoNafithali\x + Luka 4.14,31. Joha. 4.43. Mat. 9.1.\x*;
\v 14 ukuze kugcwaliseke okwakhulunywa ngumprofethi uIsaya, ukuthi:
\v 15 Ilizwe lakoZebuloni lelizwe lakoNafithali\x + Isa. 9.1,2.\x*, \add e\add*ndlel\add eni\add* yaselwandle, ngaphetsheya kweJordani\x + 10.5.\x*, iGalili labezizwe\x + 10.5.\x*,
\v 16 abantu ababehlezi emnyameni babonile ukukhanya okukhulu, lababehlezi elizweni lethunzini lokufa ukukhanya kuphumele kubo.
\s UJesu uqala ukutshumayela
\p
\v 17 Kusukela kulesosikhathi uJesu waqala ukutshumayela lokuthi\x + Mark. 1.14,15.\x*: Phendukani; ngoba umbuso wamazulu ususondele\x + 3.2.\x*.
\s Ukubizwa kwabafundi bakuqala
\p
\v 18 Kwathi uJesu ehambahamba\x + Mark. 1.16-20. Luka 5.2-11. Joha. 1.40-42.\x* elwandle lweGalili wabona izelamani ezimbili\x + 15.29. Mark. 1.16; 7.31. Joha. 6.1. Luka 5.1.\x*, uSimoni othiwa nguPetro\x + Joha. 1.42.\x*, loAndreya umfowabo, bephosela imbule olwandle; ngoba babengabagoli benhlanzi.
\v 19 Wasesithi kubo: Ngilandelani, njalo ngizalenza libe ngabagoli babantu.
\v 20 Bahle-ke batshiya amambule bamlandela\x + 19.27. Mark. 10.28. Luka 18.28.\x*.
\v 21 Eseqhubeke esuka lapho, wabona ezinye izelamani ezimbili, uJakobe okaZebediya loJohane umfowabo, besemkhunjini kanye loZebediya uyise, belungisa amambule abo; wasebabiza.
\v 22 Njalo bahle batshiya umkhumbi loyise bamlandela.
\s UJesu usebenza elizweni leGalili
\p
\v 23 UJesu wasebhoda iGalili yonke, efundisa emasinagogeni abo\x + 9.35; 13.54. Mark. 1.21,39. Luka 4.15,44.\x*, etshumayela ivangeli lombuso\x + 9.35; 24.14. Mark. 1.14. Mat. 8.12; 13.19,38,52.\x*, eselapha sonke isifo lobuthakathaka bonke ebantwini\x + Mark. 1.34.\x*.
\v 24 Indumela yakhe yasiphumela kuyo yonke iSiriya\x + Mark. 7.26.\x*; basebeletha kuye bonke abagulayo, ababephethwe yizifo ngezifo lobuhlungu\x + Luka 16.23,28.\x*, lababengenwe ngamadimoni\x + 8.16,28,33; 9.32; 12.22; 15.22. Mark. 1.32; 5.15,16,18. Luka 8.36. Joha. 10.21.\x*, lababelezithuthwane\x + 17.15.\x*, lababewome umhlubulo; wasebasilisa.
\v 25 Amaxuku amakhulu asemlandela evela eGalili\x + Mark. 1.45; 3.7. Luka 6.17.\x* leDikapolisi leJerusalema leJudiya langaphetsheya kweJordani\x + Mark. 5.20; 7.31.\x*.